#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Help System Handbook"
msgstr "&kde; abisüsteemi käsiraamat"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help System"
msgstr "Abisüsteem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The help system is designed to make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems "
"(<application>man</application> and <application>info</application>) simple, "
"as well as the user documentation of applications including &plasma-"
"workspaces; from the &kde; community (&XML;)."
msgstr ""
"Abisüsteemi eesmärk on muuta tavapäraste &UNIX; abisüsteemide "
"(<application>man</application> ja <application>info</application>) ning "
"rakenduste käsiraamatute, sealhulgas &kde; kogukonna pakutavate &plasma-"
"workspaces; käsiraamatute (&XML;), kasutamine hõlpsaks ja lihtsaks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All applications (including &plasma-workspaces;) from the &kde; community "
"come fully documented, thanks to the efforts of the Documentation team. If "
"you are interested in helping with the documentation efforts, join the "
"<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">mailing "
"list</ulink> and write to the team at <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</"
"email>. No experience is required, just enthusiasm and patience."
msgstr ""
"Kõik &kde; kogukonna pakutavad rakendused (kaasa arvatud &plasma-"
"workspaces;) on tänu dokumentatsioonimeeskonna tööle täielikult "
"dokumenteeritud. Kui soovid oma abi pakkuda, ühine <ulink url=\"https://mail."
"kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">postiloendiga</ulink> ja kirjuta "
"meeskonnale aadressil <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</email>. Selleks ei ole "
"tegelikult vaja isegi kogemust, piisab entusiasmist ja kannatlikkusest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
#| "language, review the information, including coordinators for each "
#| "language team, on the <ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org\">Localization web "
#| "site</ulink>."
msgid ""
"If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
"language, review the information, including coordinators for each language "
"team, on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">Localization web site</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid kaasa aidata &kde; dokumentatsiooni tõlkimisele oma emakeelde, "
"siis leiab täpsemat infot, sealhulgas tõlkemeeskondade koordinaatorid, "
"<ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org\">lokaliseerimise veebileheküljelt</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking Help"
msgstr "Abiteksti väljakutsumine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "&khelpcenter; can be called in several ways:"
msgstr "&khelpcenter; on võimalik välja kutsuda mitmel moel:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu"
msgstr "Menüüst <guimenu>Abi</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common will probably be from within an application. Choose "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Application</replaceable> Handbook</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to open that application's handbook."
msgstr ""
"See on tõenäoliselt kõige levinum viis mingi rakenduse kasutamise puhul. "
"Antud rakenduse abifaili kasutamiseks kasuta selle menüüd <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Abi</guimenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>Rakenduse</"
"replaceable> käsiraamat</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Application Launcher"
msgstr "Rakenduste käivitajast"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the big <guiicon>K</guiicon> in your panel, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem> from the <guimenuitem>Applications</"
"guimenuitem> tab or type <userinput>help</userinput> followed by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem>. This will open &khelpcenter; with the "
"default start page."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa paneelil suurel <guiicon>K</guiicon>-tähel ja vali seal kaardil "
"<guimenuitem>Rakendused</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Abi</guimenuitem> või "
"kirjuta <userinput>help</userinput> pärast <guimenuitem>Abi</guimenuitem> "
"valimist. See avab Abikeskuse avalehekülje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the command line"
msgstr "Käsurealt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; may be started using a &URL; to display a file. &URL;s have "
"been added for <command>info</command> and <command>man</command> pages "
"also. You can use them as follows:"
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter;e saab faili näitamiseks käivitada &URL;-iga. Vastavad &URL;-id "
"on lisatud ka <command>info</command> ja <command>man</command> "
"kasutamiseks. Käsud võivad olla järgmised:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application help file"
msgstr "Rakenduse abifail"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the &kwrite; help file, at the contents page."
msgstr "See avab &kwrite;'i abifaili sisukorra."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "A local &URL;"
msgstr "Kohalik &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Man page"
msgstr "Manuaalilehekülg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "An Info page"
msgstr "Infolehekülg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking <command>khelpcenter</command> with no parameters opens the default "
"start page."
msgstr ""
"Käsk <command>khelpcenter</command> ilma täpsustuseta avab abikeskuse "
"avalehekülje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface"
msgstr "&khelpcenter;e kasutajaliides"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface consists of two panes of information."
msgstr "&khelpcenter; koosneb kahest infopaneelist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar and menus are explained further in <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Tööriistaribade ja menüüde kasutamist seletab lähemalt <xref linkend=\"menu-"
"and-toolbar-ref\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Documents contain their own navigation tools, enabling you to move either "
"sequentially through a document, using <guilabel>Next</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Previous</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> links, or "
"to move around in a less structured manner, using hyperlinks."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentidel on omaette navigeerimisvahendid, mis võimaldavad liikuda "
"erinevate dokumentide juurde, kasutates viitu <guilabel>Järgmine</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Eelmine</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Sisukord</guilabel> või siis "
"hüperlinke kasutades otse vajaliku dokumendi juurde."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Links can take you to other parts of the same document, or to a different "
"document, and you can use the <guiicon>Back</guiicon> (Left pointing arrow) "
"or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> (Right pointing arrow) icons on the toolbar to "
"move through the documents you have viewed in this session."
msgstr ""
"Viidad võivad sind viia sama dokumendi teise osa või hoopis teise dokumendi "
"juurde. Seansi ajal kasutatud dokumentide vahel saab saab liikuda, kui "
"kasutada tööriistaribal ikoone <guiicon>Tagasi</guiicon> (vasakule osutav "
"nool) ja <guiicon>Edasi</guiicon> (paremale osutav nool)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two panes display the contents of the help system, and the help files "
"themselves, on the left and right respectively."
msgstr ""
"Kaks paneeli näitavad vasakul abisüsteemi sisukorda ja paremal abifaile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Pane"
msgstr "Paneel Sisukord"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane in &khelpcenter; is displayed on the left hand side of the "
"window. As you might expect, you can move the splitter bar, to make sure you "
"can comfortably read the contents of either pane."
msgstr ""
"Paneel Sisukord paikneb &khelpcenter;es akna vasakus ääres. "
"Enesestmõistetavalt on kahe paneeli vahel liigutatav piire, mis muudab "
"ükspuha kumba paneeli lugemise väga mugavaks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane is further divided into three tabs, one containing a <link "
"linkend=\"contents-tab\">tree view</link> showing all the help information "
"&khelpcenter; is aware of, and the other contains the &kde; <link linkend="
"\"kde-glossary\">glossary</link> of terms. On the third tab you can "
"configure the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Paneel Sisukord jaguneb kolmeks kaardiks, millest üks sisaldab <link linkend="
"\"contents-tab\">puuvaadet</link>, mis näitab kogu abiinfot, mida "
"&khelpcenter; üldse pakub, ning teine &kde; mõistete <link linkend=\"kde-"
"glossary\">sõnaraamatut</link>. Kolmandal kaardil saab seadistada "
"<guilabel>otsimisvalikuid</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Kaart Sisukord"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab contains the following default top "
"level entries in the tree view:"
msgstr ""
"Kaart <guilabel>Sisukord</guilabel> sisaldab puuvaates järgmisi tipptasandi "
"vaikekirjeid:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fundamentals"
msgstr "Põhialused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fundamentals introduce you to the many features of the &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications; and describe many common tasks you can "
"perform in all &applications;."
msgstr ""
"Põhialused tutvustavad paljusid &plasma-workspaces; ja &applications; "
"omadusi ning kirjeldavad levinumaid ülesandeid, mida saab ette võtta kõigis "
"rakendustes."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Manual"
msgstr "Plasma käsiraamat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &plasma; Manual is the documentation for the &plasma-workspaces;."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; käsiraamat dokumenteerib kõige nähtavama osa, kogu töölaua "
"tuumikliidese (&plasma-workspaces;)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Abi internetis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A page with links to online help and additional information provided by the "
"&kde; community."
msgstr ""
"Siin leiab mitmeid võimalusi saada internetist abi ja lisateavet, mida pakub "
"&kde; kogukond."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Manuals"
msgstr "Rakenduste käsiraamatud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Native &kde; application documentation. All &kde; applications have "
"documentation in &XML; format, which are converted to <acronym>HTML</"
"acronym> when you view them. This section lists all the &kde; applications "
"with a brief description and a link to the full application documentation."
msgstr ""
"&kde; omarakenduste dokumentatsioon. Kõigi &kde; rakenduste dokumentatsioon "
"on &XML;-vormingus, mis teisendatakse <acronym>HTML</acronym>-vormingusse, "
"kui sa seda vaatad. See sektsioon toob ära kõik &kde; rakendused, annab "
"nende kohta lühikirjelduse ja viitab rakenduse põhjalikule "
"dokumentatsioonile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The applications are displayed in a tree structure that echoes the default "
"structure of the <guimenu>K</guimenu> menu, making it easy to find the "
"application you are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Rakendused on esitatud puuna, mis vastab <guimenu>K</guimenu>-menüü "
"vaikestruktuurile, muutes nii lihtsamaks selle rakenduse leidmise, mille "
"kohta sa infot soovisid."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Settings Modules</guilabel> entities"
msgstr "<guilabel>Seadistuste moodulite</guilabel> kirjed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide a list of links to various modules in the &systemsettings; "
"application or to modules for &konqueror;, Filemanager or Browser."
msgstr ""
"Annab ülevaate erinevatest moodulitest, mida pakuvad Süsteemi seadistused "
"või ka &konqueror;i, failihalduri või brauseri moodulid."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "KInfoCenter Modules"
msgstr "Infokeskuse moodulid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains a list of links to various KInfocenter modules documentation."
msgstr "Sisaldab viitu erinevate KDE infokeskuse moodulite dokumentatsioonile."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "KIO Workers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains a list of links to various <acronym>KIO</acronym> modules "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Sisaldab viitu erinevate <acronym>KIO</acronym>-moodulite dokumentatsioonile."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "&UNIX; manual pages"
msgstr "&UNIX;-i man-leheküljed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; man pages are the traditional on-line documentation format for &UNIX; "
"systems. Most programs on your system will have a man page. In addition, man "
"pages exist for programming functions and file formats."
msgstr ""
"&UNIX;-i manuaalileheküljed on &UNIX;-i süsteemide traditsiooniline "
"dokumentatsioonivorming. Süsteemi enamikul rakendustel on olemas oma man-"
"lehekülg. Lisaks sellele on man-lehekülgi ka mitmesuguste käskude ja "
"failivormingute kohta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollkeeper"
msgstr "Scrollkeeper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional non-&kde; documentation installed on your system."
msgstr "Täiendav süsteemi paigaldatud &kde;-väline dokumentatsioon."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Info Pages"
msgstr "Infoleheküljed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TeXinfo documentation is used by many &GNU; applications, including "
"<command>gcc</command> (the C/C++ compiler), <command>emacs</command>, and "
"many others."
msgstr ""
"TeXinfo dokumentatsiooni kasutavad paljud &GNU; rakendused, sealhulgas "
"<command>gcc</command> (C/C++ kompilaator), <command>emacs</command> ja "
"paljud teised."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Kaart <guilabel>Otsimisvalikud</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the help files is fairly intuitive, enter the word(s) you wish to "
"search for in the text box, choose your options (if any), and press "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The results display in the viewer pane to the "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Failides otsimine on üpris loomupärane: sisesta vaid sõnad, mida soovid "
"leida, otsimiskasti, määra valikud (kui neid on või kui neid kasutada tahad) "
"ja klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Otsi</guibutton>. Tulemusi näeb paremal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is not case sensitive, &ie; uppercase and lowercase characters are "
"considered the same. For example, if you search for <quote>Shortcut</quote>, "
"results that contain <quote>shortcut</quote> will be returned as well."
msgstr ""
"Otsing ei ole tõstutundlik, mis tähendab, et suuri ja väikesi tähti ei "
"eristata. Kui näiteks otsid sõna <quote>Kiirklahv</quote>, näidatakse ka "
"kõiki kohti, kus seisab <quote>kiirklahv</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "The options available are:"
msgstr "Võimalikud on järgmised valikud:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Meetod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose how to search for multiple words. If you choose <guilabel>and</"
"guilabel>, results are returned only if all your search terms are included "
"in the page. <guilabel>or</guilabel> returns results if <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> of the search terms are found."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata, kuidas otsida mitut sõna. Kui valida <guilabel>ja</"
"guilabel>, näidatakse tulemusi ainult juhul, kui leheküljel leiduvad kõik "
"sinu otsingusõnad. Kui valida <guilabel>või</guilabel>, näidatakse tulemusi, "
"kui leitakse <emphasis>kas või mõni</emphasis> otsingusõna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your searches are not returning the results you expect, check carefully "
"you haven't excluded the wrong search term with an erroneous setting."
msgstr ""
"Kui otsing ei anna sellist tulemust, nagu oleksid oodanud, kontrolli väga "
"hoolikalt, et ei oleks välistanud vajalikku sõna mõne väära valikuga."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max. results"
msgstr "Maks. tulemusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Determines the maximum number of results returned from your search."
msgstr "Määrab otsinguga leitud tulemuste näitamise maksimaalse arvu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope selection"
msgstr "Ulatuse valik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to select the sections where the search will be done. The "
"available options quickly select the most common option, while "
"<guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem> allows one to select single sections."
msgstr ""
"Sellega saab paika panna sektsioone, kus otsida. Saadaolevate valikutega "
"saab kiiresti paika panna kõige levinuma võimaluse, <guimenuitem>Kohandatud</"
"guimenuitem> aga lubab valida sektsioone ükshaaval."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>Man</application> and <application>Info</application> "
"sections"
msgstr ""
"<application>Man</application> ja <application>Info</application> sektsioonid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man pages are the standard &UNIX; manual pages, and have been in use for "
"many years on many operating systems. They are extremely thorough, and are "
"the very best place to get information about most &UNIX; commands and "
"applications. When people say <quote>RTFM</quote>, the Manual they are "
"referring to is very often the man page."
msgstr ""
"Man-leheküljed on standardsed &UNIX;-i manuaalileheküljed, mida on juba "
"aastaid kasutatud paljudes operatsioonidesüsteemides. Need on väga "
"põhjalikud ja seetõttu parim koht, kust hankida infot &UNIX;-i käskude ja "
"rakenduste kohta. Kui öeldakse <quote>RTFM</quote>, peetakse manuaali all "
"enamasti silmas just man-lehekülge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The man pages are not perfect. They tend to be in depth, but also extremely "
"technical, often written by developers, and for developers. In some cases "
"this makes them somewhat unfriendly, if not downright impossible for many "
"users to understand. They are, however, the best source of solid information "
"on most command line applications, and very often the only source."
msgstr ""
"Man-leheküljed ei ole küll ideaalsed. Nad on enamasti põhjalikud, aga samas "
"väga tehnilised, sest neid on tihtipeale kirjutajad arendajad - teistele "
"arendajatele. Mõnikord muudab see nad väga raskesti mõistetavaks või isegi "
"täiesti mõistetamatuks nii-öelda tavakasutajale. Siiski on see parim koht, "
"kust hankida infot enamiku käsurearakenduste kohta, ja väga tihti ka ainus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you've ever wondered what the number is when people write things like "
"man(1) it means which section of the manual the item is in. You will see "
"&khelpcenter; uses the numbers to divide the very many man pages into their "
"own sections, making it easier for you to find the information you're "
"looking for, if you're just browsing."
msgstr ""
"Kui sa oled kunagi hämmastunult mõelnud, mida küll tähendab see, kui kirjas "
"seisab näiteks man(1), siis see tähendab seda, millises manuaali sektsioonis "
"viidatu paikneb. Ka &khelpcenter; kasutab numbreid, et jagada man-"
"lehekülgede hiigelhulk teatud sektsioonideks, mis võimaldab lihtsamaks leida "
"just seda infot, mida sul vaja läheb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also available are the Info pages, intended to be a replacement for the man "
"pages. The maintainer of some applications no longer update the man pages, "
"so if there is both a man page and an info page available, the info page is "
"probably the most recent. Most applications have one or the other though. If "
"the application you are looking for help on is a &GNU; utility, you will "
"most likely find it has an info page, not a man page."
msgstr ""
"Kasutada saab ka info-lehekülgi, mis oma aja arvamuse kohaselt pidanuks "
"asendama man-leheküljed. Mõningate rakenduste hooldajad ei hoolitse enam man-"
"lehekülgede eest, nii et kui saadaval on nii info- kui ka man-leheküljed, on "
"esimesed arvatavasti uuemad. Enamik rakendusi pakub siiski vaid ainult üht "
"või teist, mitte mõlemat. Kui uuritav rakendus peaks olema mõni &GNU; "
"rakendus, siis on tõenäoline, et see pakub vaid info-lehekülge, mitte man-"
"lehekülge."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating inside the <application>Info</application> pages"
msgstr "Liikumine <application>info</application>-lehekülgedel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info documents are arranged hierarchically with each page called a node. All "
"info documents have a <guilabel>Top</guilabel> node, &ie; the opening page. "
"You can return to the <guilabel>Top</guilabel> of an info document by "
"pressing <guilabel>Top</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Info-dokumendid on korrastatud hierarhiliselt, lehekülgi kutsutakse siin "
"sõlmedeks. Kõigil info-lehekülgedel on sõlm <guilabel>Top</guilabel>, &ie; "
"avalehekülg. Info-lehekülje \"tippu\" pääseb klõpsuga viidal <guilabel>Top</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton> are used to "
"move to the previous/next page at the current level of the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"Hierarhia samal tasemel eelmisele ja järgmisele leheküljele liikumiseks saab "
"kasutada viitu <guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a menu item within a document moves you to a lower level in the "
"hierarchy. You may move up the hierarchy by pressing <guibutton>Up</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Klõps menüüelemendil dokumendi sees viib hierarhia järgmisele astmele. "
"Tagasi ülespoole pääseb viidaga <guibutton>Up</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man is treated similarly to info, with the section index being the Top node "
"and each man page on the level below. Man entries are one page long."
msgstr ""
"Man-lehekülgede kasutamine on sarnane info-lehekülgede kasutamisega, ka seal "
"on sektsiooni indeks \"Top\" ja iga man-lehekülg asub taseme võrra allpool. "
"Manuaalikirjed on ühe lehekülje pikkused."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kde; glossary"
msgstr "&kde; sõnaraamat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The glossary provides a quick reference point, where you can look up the "
"definitions of words that may be unfamiliar to you. These range from &kde; "
"specific applications and technologies, through to general &UNIX; computing "
"terms."
msgstr ""
"Sõnaraamat on mõeldud kiireks viitematerjaliks, kus võib leida seletuse sõna "
"kohta, mida sa varem ei teadnud. Mõisted ulatuvad &kde; spetsiifilistest "
"rakendustest ja tehnoloogiatest &UNIX;-i üldiste terminiteni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the left hand pane you will see a tree view, with two choices: "
"<guilabel>Alphabetically</guilabel> or <guilabel>By Topic</guilabel>. Both "
"contain the same entries, sorted differently, to allow you to quickly find "
"the item of interest."
msgstr ""
"Vasakul paneelil on puuvaade kahe valikuga: <guilabel>Tähestiku järgi</"
"guilabel> ja <guilabel>Teema järgi</guilabel>. Mõlemad sisaldavad "
"ühesuguseid mõisteid, mis on erinevalt korraldatud, võimaldamaks kiiresti "
"leida huvipakkuva termini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate down the tree views to the left, and items you select will be "
"displayed on the right."
msgstr ""
"Liikudes vasakul esitatud puus vajaliku kohani, avaneb paremal otsitava "
"mõiste seletus."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus and toolbar"
msgstr "Menüüd ja tööriistariba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; has a very minimal interface, allowing you to concentrate on "
"getting help rather than learning how to use the help browser."
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter;e kasutajaliides on väga lihtne, mis võimaldab abikeskuse "
"talituspõhimõtete tundmaõppimise asemel keskenduda abi saamisele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icons available to you in the toolbar are as follows:"
msgstr "Tööriistaribal kasutatakse järgmisi ikoone:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar Icons"
msgstr "Tööriistariba ikoonid"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "Sisukord"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490 index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the main start page of &khelpcenter;."
msgstr "Avab &abikeskus;e avalehekülje."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Tagasi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous page you viewed. Click the check mark right to the icon. "
"This displays a list of previously viewed pages. Selecting one will take you "
"directly back to that page."
msgstr ""
"Liigub tagasi eelmisele vaadatud leheküljele. Kui klõpsata ikoonist paremal "
"asuvale linnukesele, ilmub nähtavale varem külastatud lehekülgede loend. "
"Sealt mõne valimisel saab liikuda otse soovitud leheküljele."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Edasi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go forward one page. This icon is only active if you have already used the "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Liigub ühe lehekülje võrra edasi. Seda saab kasutada ainult siis, kui varem "
"on kasutatud ikooni <guiicon>Tagasi</guiicon>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopeeri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy text to the clipboard to be pasted in another application."
msgstr ""
"Kopeerib teksti lõikepuhvrisse, kust seda saab asetada mõnda muusse "
"rakendusse."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Otsi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words within the currently visible page."
msgstr "Otsib sõna või sõnu parajasti vaadataval leheküljel."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase Font Sizes"
msgstr "Suurenda fonti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase the size of the text in the viewer pane."
msgstr "Suurendab tekstisuurust vaateleheküljel."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease Font Sizes"
msgstr "Vähenda fonti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decrease the size of the text in the viewer pane. This icon is only enabled "
"if you have previously enlarged the text."
msgstr ""
"Vähendab tekstisuurust vaateleheküljel. See toimib ainult siis, kui varem on "
"teksti suurendatud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus contain the following entries:"
msgstr "Menüüdes esinevad järgmised kirjed:"

